players.name: Ademola Lookman
players.summary: Ademola Lookman Olajade Alade Ayoola Lookman is a professional footballer who plays as a second striker for Serie A club Atalanta. Born in England, he plays for the Nigeria national team. He is primarily a winger, often playing on the left wing, but also effective on the right. He is known for his pace, dribbling, and ability to cut inside to shoot.

Widely regarded as one of the best strikers in the world. Osimhen is known for his explosive pace, physical strength, aerial ability, and clinical finishing.
